parameters: \C[23][Luna]\C[0] Noah, I'm sorry. I couldn't get my hands on the Gra herbs...

\C[29][Noah]\C[0] I heard from Becky. You gave them to the resistance soldiers from
another village, right?

\C[29][Noah]\C[0] Luna, you're so kind. I don't mind at all. That's why I like you so
much.
\C[29][Noah]\C[0] Actually, I called you here today because I really wanted to see you.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Yeah... I wanted to see you too.

\C[29][Noah]\C[0] Haha, it's kind of embarrassing, isn't it? We've just become lovers,
after all.
\C[29][Noah]\C[0] Oops, let's get to the main topic.
\C[29][Noah]\C[0] I've found out about Regnus Grahardt's whereabouts.
\C[29][Noah]\C[0] It seems he appeared in the 'Southern' lava cave.

\C[29][Noah]\C[0] Apparently, Regnus Grahardt saved some local girls who were playing
in Southern and almost got caught in the lava.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] How did they know the person who saved them was Regnus Grahardt?

\C[29][Noah]\C[0] There was someone from the village who had been saved by Regnus
Grahardt before at the scene.

\C[29][Noah]\C[0] That person wanted to thank Regnus and tried to talk to him, but he
left quickly... They're certain it was Regnus Grahardt himself.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Of course, I'm going to the 'Southern' flame cave.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Right now, all I can do is chase after Regnus Grahardt's shadow.

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] If you continue this senseless slaughter, I'll use whatever means
necessary to defeat you.

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] "I will definitely find Regnus Grahardt," her expression changed for
a moment. I've never seen Lucia with that look before.

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] I don't know who Regnus Grahardt is. But right now, it feels like
that's all I have to bet on.

\C[29][Noah]\C[0] Luna, please don't push yourself too hard. The generals of Valentina
and Lucia are after you. I'm worried about you.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] It's okay... I'm okay, Noah. But if I don't do it, no one else will.
Luna and the others headed towards the "Southern Cave."
